Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,356)\3a&H5F&}{\fad(871,1052)}First Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.40,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:13.80,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why did my face get so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why did my heart beat so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,My face is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:37.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,How weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boys in class 4 are slacking on the culture festival preparations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ranking the first year girls in beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They should look in the mirror, before talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should do a boys ranking too, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na-no-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's your top choice of the boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know the boys in the other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Miyauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you went home with him the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get so close to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, we had to stay late to finish up some executive committee work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way you desperately defend yourself makes it even more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It must be embarrassing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone... everyone's just kidding around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its fine. I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... would you read this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something like a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... I just spoke to you for the first time the other day... It's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from this guy named Asano in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... It is... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't mean I dislike you, Miyauchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I put this... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well he doesn't look like a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's nice, though he has a pretty plain face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanoka, come here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's stop spying on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you say, but it actually bothers you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably just playing around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you run away? It was your chance to talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's always tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to look around the festival with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try going out with him for a day, and see if you want to go out with him for real after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... but what... do you do when you ''go out'' with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a whole bunch of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like walk home together, visit each others houses or walk through a park...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A park?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you get a boyfriend you'll be able to grow out of your brother complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a brother complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... About tomorrow's culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you come too, Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you won't get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem like a bad person, but the letter seems so easygoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that maybe he's just making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't go out with a boy I've never even talked to before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know this boy very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's saying you should try hanging out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Futaba-chan said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't show me letters like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may look like he's just being casual but he might be pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you show such important letters so casually to a third person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to talk to someone about it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if he doesn't seem like a bad guy, try going out with him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if he doesn't seem like a bad guy, try going out with him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if you think you guys get along, go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it'll go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... you got really mad the other day when Miyauchi-kun just walked me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that. I won't treat you like a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my own problem. I can decide on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.99,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:52.39,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Besides... Onii-chan... has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... I can't really think about going out with anyone right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that it'd be cool if we could hang out together, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there someone else you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually kind of busy with my class haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've troubled you, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that has to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Do Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photo of my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ended up not coming to the culture festival, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see what kind of prince this brother you're always talking about looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He isn't very good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His beard is all bushy and he kind of smells like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He smells bad? What does he smell like? A weird smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you put this in the wash?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Does it smell that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really stink, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.64,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The scores are 3 runs apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.87,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the 9th with 2 outs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.26,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Runners on 1st and 3rd base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.73,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The batter is Yoshimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.34,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Today, he's 2 for 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.90,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If he hits a home run, the score will be tied but-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.30,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's hit hard, down the first base line and... it's foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.73,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It had the distance, but it sliced right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:01.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The closer, Ueda, is warming up in the bullpen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.92,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,but the manager, Oomori, shows no move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.05,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,2nd pitch, he hits it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.83,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He hits a line drive straight into right field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.54,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The runner on 3rd comes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.18,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Runner on 1st rounds 3rd and heads for home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you help me with my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot what I studied in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're making me lose my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you have to do for that one is put it in the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You messed up on the first calculation for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see. I do that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... The homework was due today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't make it on time! The teacher's going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:39.13,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,If Futaba-chan and the others saw Onii-chan... what would they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:48.47,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess Onii-chan isn't really that cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're early!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your sister making dinner at home or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not even bothered when I bring up his younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:18.90,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan always looks upset, and I don't really know what goes on in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.56,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He's mean and grumpy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.86,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,and yet sometimes he's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.89,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,and it surprises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So umm..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go with that guy who wrote you the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun at the culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have something on your mind, feel free to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, if you don't know how to go out with him or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you're having a hard time with things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turned him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Did you worry about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's 10 years too early for you to be getting a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't treat me like a kid any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of adult would swing a bag around so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you following me the whole way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw you on top of that hill and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How sick! You were looking at me secretly and laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's fine, something Nanoka would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just called me Nanoka for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You always say "hey you" so condescendingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not really being condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm always the one that gets surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unfair...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love you Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do yo mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're weird... blushing like that! So weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is she saying...?
